<h3>Second Pass—Combining Lines into Blocks</h3>

<p>So now we have a list of line types. We need to look for things such
as the setext-style heading. And it turns out that structure
decomposition lets us do this pretty painlessly. Here&rsquo;s the code for
the headings:</p>

