<p>There are exceptions, of course. There are a number of PEG <a href="https://github.com/jgm/peg-markdown">markdown</a> <a href="http://hasseg.org/peg-markdown-highlight/">parsers</a>, and some cool implementations in <a href="http://hackage.haskell.org/package/markdown-0.1.0.1/docs/Text-Markdown.html">Haskell</a> and (my favorite) <a href="https://github.com/gildor478/ocaml-markdown">OCaml</a>.<a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote">&#8617;</a></p></li>
